Locale::Codes::LangExt_Retired(3pm) Perl Programmers Reference Guide Locale::Codes::LangExt_Retired(3pm)

NAME

Locale::Codes::LangExt_Retired - retired langext codes for the Locale::Codes::LangExt module

SYNOPSIS

This module contains data used by the Locale::Codes::LangExt module. It is not intended to be used directly, and contains no calleable routines.

AUTHOR

See Locale::Codes for full author history.
